Dialogue: 69,0:00:03.44,0:00:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really comin' down now.
Dialogue: 69,0:00:05.97,0:00:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather prediction was off, Hizuru.
Dialogue: 69,0:00:09.16,0:00:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Predictions, presumptions, precognitions—
Dialogue: 69,0:00:13.69,0:00:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't nothin' with the word "pre" attached to it ever been right.
Dialogue: 69,0:00:18.28,0:00:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We really goin' down there?
Dialogue: 69,0:00:19.97,0:00:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I have a bad feeling about this too.
Dialogue: 69,0:00:23.55,0:00:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just hope my premonition proves false.
Dialogue: 69,0:00:28.26,0:00:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 69,0:00:30.09,0:00:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stop!
Dialogue: 69,0:00:36.67,0:00:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 69,0:00:50.34,0:00:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,These things are targeting Ushio relentlessly.
Dialogue: 69,0:00:54.28,0:00:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They basically haven't attacked me at all.
Dialogue: 69,0:01:01.17,0:01:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio?!
Dialogue: 69,0:01:04.15,0:01:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your arm hurt?
Dialogue: 69,0:01:08.00,0:01:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's no use. We can't go any farther.
Dialogue: 69,0:01:11.98,0:01:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer in the way! Move!
Dialogue: 69,0:01:14.30,0:01:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou!
Dialogue: 69,0:01:17.03,0:01:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice!
Dialogue: 69,0:01:18.01,0:01:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why you brought the spray along?
Dialogue: 69,0:01:20.09,0:01:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell yeah! Working just like I thought!
Dialogue: 69,0:01:21.94,0:01:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't no creature alive not scared of fire!
Dialogue: 69,0:01:24.90,0:01:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya okay, Ushio?\NWe can still turn back!
Dialogue: 69,0:01:28.79,0:01:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 69,0:01:30.52,0:01:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Charge forward!
Dialogue: 69,0:01:32.33,0:01:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate half-assing things!
Dialogue: 69,0:01:34.53,0:01:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 69,0:01:35.99,0:01:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei, I'll open a path!
Dialogue: 69,0:01:38.96,0:01:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You take care of Ushio!
Dialogue: 69,0:01:41.47,0:01:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Already on it!
Dialogue: 69,0:01:50.88,0:01:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ryuunosuke!
Dialogue: 69,0:01:52.63,0:01:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me if yer gonna shoot!
Dialogue: 69,0:01:54.85,0:01:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go deaf!
Dialogue: 69,0:01:56.10,0:01:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but if I took the time to speak, \Nwe would have died.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:00.92,0:02:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, to think the Shadows were lurking under the island...
Dialogue: 69,0:02:04.92,0:02:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:06.43,0:02:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Their numbers are increasing.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:08.63,0:02:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We're getting close to their nest.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:10.99,0:02:10.99,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{OP}
