Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:44.10,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)\t(4287,4287,\bord5\blur5)}Trapped in the eddy of what I know will be my fate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:48.31,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)\t(\xbord20\ybord0)}I'm sure I won't be coming back from the sea as I was
