Dialogue: 69,0:03:49.46,0:03:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where's Shin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:53.59,ep title,,0,0,1,,{\bord7\c&HC0A038&\alpha&H30&\blur7}Time to Feed
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.75,0:03:53.59,ep title,,0,0,1,,{\blur0.5}Time to Feed
Dialogue: 69,0:03:51.05,0:03:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know he went to see Sou, \Nbut I can't reach either of them.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:55.42,0:03:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tokiko ain't picking up neither.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:58.50,0:04:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and come back, Shin.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:02.81,0:04:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Shadow Sickness.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:04.18,0:04:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not only is Sis dead, Shiori disappeared too.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:07.51,0:04:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And now something's even happened to Shin!
Dialogue: 69,0:04:22.77,0:04:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,These are Shiori's hair ties!
Dialogue: 69,0:04:27.51,0:04:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:29.20,0:04:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei is over here.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:33.19,0:04:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 69,0:04:37.08,0:04:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close—
Dialogue: 69,0:04:38.79,0:04:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mio!
Dialogue: 69,0:04:39.87,0:04:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Tetsu! Sorry!
Dialogue: 69,0:04:42.01,0:04:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya can't just jump out like that!
Dialogue: 69,0:04:44.24,0:04:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's got ya all riled up?
Dialogue: 69,0:04:46.33,0:04:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiori was just here! Did ya see her?
Dialogue: 69,0:04:50.49,0:04:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 69,0:04:51.42,0:04:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw her? Where? Where?!
Dialogue: 69,0:04:54.79,0:04:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She ran toward where ya just came from.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:57.69,0:05:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? Yer the only one I saw come runnin' my way.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:12.81,0:05:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiori?!
Dialogue: 69,0:05:17.88,0:05:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-She's gone...
Dialogue: 69,0:05:21.29,0:05:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 69,0:05:24.23,0:05:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The manhole cover's open.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:27.92,0:05:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei is over here.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:31.20,0:05:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?\NIs Shin in here?
Dialogue: 69,0:05:39.20,0:05:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no. No, no, no!
Dialogue: 69,0:05:41.59,0:05:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If weren't her!
Dialogue: 69,0:05:42.49,0:05:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't no way a grade-schooler went in there!
Dialogue: 69,0:05:46.44,0:05:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, normally...
Dialogue: 69,0:05:48.20,0:05:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But what if that was Shiori's Shadow?
Dialogue: 69,0:05:51.86,0:05:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tetsu.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:52.16,0:05:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No way.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:53.44,0:05:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But I ain't said nothin' yet!
Dialogue: 69,0:05:55.45,0:05:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya want me to look inside, right?
Dialogue: 69,0:05:57.32,0:06:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't happenin'! I'm busy!
Dialogue: 69,0:06:00.63,0:06:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm goin' to the city to drink.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:03.05,0:06:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If I show up in my cool uniform stinkin' and lookin' like a sewer rat,
Dialogue: 69,0:06:05.44,0:06:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Erika will hate me!
Dialogue: 69,0:06:07.60,0:06:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya'd choose a barfly over a human life?
Dialogue: 69,0:06:10.82,0:06:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, we don't know for sure.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:13.39,0:06:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya'd be a hero.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:14.95,0:06:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 69,0:06:15.94,0:06:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Just imagine the newspaper articles about the hero who saved the missing girl.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:21.18,0:06:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya'd be famous over night.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:23.45,0:06:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And Erika, why, she'd be head-over-heels for ya.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:26.07,0:06:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But if ya don't wanna go, that's fine.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:28.05,0:06:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't try to stop me.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:29.80,0:06:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go in alone if I have to.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:31.25,0:06:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow my lead.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:33.50,0:06:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This ain't 'cause I wanna be a hero or popular, ya hear?
Dialogue: 69,0:06:36.27,0:06:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:37.34,0:06:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an ally of justice, y'know.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:39.96,0:06:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanna find Shiori.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:43.08,0:06:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank ya.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:44.75,0:06:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess even selfish motives are better than doin' nothin' at all.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:47.59,0:06:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's harsh, Mio.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:58.68,0:07:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We somehow managed to escape.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:00.96,0:07:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but what is this place?
Dialogue: 69,0:07:04.88,0:07:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's weirder than anywhere we've been so far.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:07.15,0:07:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:08.41,0:07:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:10.61,0:07:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 69,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coral.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:14.42,0:07:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How can ocean life be living on land?
Dialogue: 69,0:07:17.54,0:07:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadows.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:18.60,0:07:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 69,0:07:19.34,0:07:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The coral, sea anemones, and barnacles—
Dialogue: 69,0:07:22.98,0:07:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all Shadows.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:25.07,0:07:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could've done all this?
Dialogue: 69,0:07:27.23,0:07:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:28.59,0:07:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But someone printed the sea here.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:35.16,0:07:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sea-water.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:36.66,0:07:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This cave must connect to the sea at some point.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:39.85,0:07:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If that means there's another exit, that's good news.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:43.22,0:07:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous to keep going, Shinpei.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:46.32,0:07:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We're out of gas.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:48.65,0:07:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're attacked again, that's it.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:54.22,0:07:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Ushio!
Dialogue: 69,0:07:55.80,0:07:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm fine.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:57.89,0:07:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just hungry.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:59.58,0:08:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes no sense.\NWe just ate an hour ago.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:04.19,0:08:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not just hunger, is it?
Dialogue: 69,0:08:07.94,0:08:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer right arm ain't healed yet, has it?
Dialogue: 69,0:08:11.76,0:08:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is damage taken by my main body.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:14.95,0:08:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Data loss, essentially.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:16.57,0:08:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to eat to fix it.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:18.53,0:08:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then just have Shinpei make ya some more rice balls.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:21.31,0:08:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Not like that.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:22.75,0:08:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need normal food.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:24.67,0:08:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to scan the original again to recover data.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:29.23,0:08:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But Ushio's ash now.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:31.48,0:08:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way to heal this wound now.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:36.35,0:08:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are ya kidding?
Dialogue: 69,0:08:38.01,0:08:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole time?
Dialogue: 69,0:08:39.27,0:08:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Have ya been holding it in ever since Shadow Mio hurt ya yesterday?
Dialogue: 69,0:08:44.20,0:08:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I only realized the truth a few minutes ago.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:46.85,0:08:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't ya tell us somethin' so important?!
Dialogue: 69,0:08:49.59,0:08:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'll just erase my right arm for now.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:53.44,0:08:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll stop the pain.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:55.92,0:08:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way to heal her?
Dialogue: 69,0:08:58.28,0:08:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That can't be!
Dialogue: 69,0:09:00.05,0:09:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's getting weaker and weaker.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:01.99,0:09:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it!
Dialogue: 69,0:09:03.08,0:09:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not gonna let her die again!
Dialogue: 69,0:09:05.41,0:09:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should I loop again?\NWill turning back time heal her?
Dialogue: 69,0:09:09.84,0:09:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But how?!
Dialogue: 69,0:09:11.45,0:09:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:13.34,0:09:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn around slowly.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:15.68,0:09:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If the two of ya make any strange movements,
Dialogue: 69,0:09:18.53,0:09:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio will pay for it with her life.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:21.54,0:09:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How are ya even here,
Dialogue: 69,0:09:25.83,0:09:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokiko?!
Dialogue: 69,0:09:29.22,0:09:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A dead end.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:30.55,0:09:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shadows came from here.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:32.84,0:09:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A secret path only for them, huh?
Dialogue: 69,0:09:35.45,0:09:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's clear.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:37.71,0:09:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shadows traveled via underground paths like the sewers to reach the island.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:42.14,0:09:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:43.51,0:09:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus there are tons of tunnels in this area dug up by the army.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:48.97,0:09:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No one knows their full extent anymore.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:52.08,0:09:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be willing to bet there are more of these secret paths.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:55.88,0:09:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, what do we do?
Dialogue: 69,0:09:57.93,0:10:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have the tools to cut through iron bars.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:01.12,0:10:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we head back up and look for another entrance?
