Dialogue: 69,0:10:04.32,0:10:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the map, we seem to be at the center of the island.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:07.96,0:10:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I doubt there are any other entrances.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:11.29,0:10:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Or at least none for humans.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:15.36,0:10:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:17.05,0:10:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The path beyond differs from the sewers.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:20.10,0:10:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably a natural cave that was here long before.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:23.77,0:10:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought it really existed. Hiruko cave.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:27.44,0:10:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 69,0:10:28.63,0:10:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandpa told me this story as a child.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:31.78,0:10:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Supposedly, underneath Hitogashima lies a giant cavern called Hiruko cave.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:38.22,0:10:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Up until halfway through the Meiji period,
Dialogue: 69,0:10:40.31,0:10:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,there was an entrance that would only appear in Hitogashima Port during low tide.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:44.91,0:10:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then during the first Sino-Japanese war, the army sealed it up while they were occupying the port.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:50.55,0:10:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was just a legend—an island folktale.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:55.67,0:11:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's said this cave is where Hiruko, the guardian of Hitogashima, settled in after washing ashore long ago.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:03.93,0:11:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hiruko legends, huh?
Dialogue: 69,0:11:06.10,0:11:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis would know more about that.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:08.36,0:11:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I change over?
Dialogue: 69,0:11:09.57,0:11:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not for now.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:12.41,0:11:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We could ask Karikiri.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:15.34,0:11:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If his old man were alive, he might have known something.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:20.42,0:11:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, we'll need a metal-cutting saw.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:23.03,0:11:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's turn back and—
Dialogue: 69,0:11:24.66,0:11:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hush.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:25.50,0:11:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, let's go back already!
Dialogue: 69,0:11:28.55,0:11:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way she's down here.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:30.79,0:11:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of what I saw earlier!
Dialogue: 69,0:11:33.25,0:11:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya saw her too, didn't ya, Tetsu?
Dialogue: 69,0:11:35.01,0:11:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, the sewer stink's all over me.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:38.68,0:11:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna need a bath before I head into town.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:41.22,0:11:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez! I'll explain things to Erika, okay?
Dialogue: 69,0:11:44.28,0:11:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll even tell her how manly ya were.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:46.74,0:11:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Ya mean it?
Dialogue: 69,0:11:49.94,0:11:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiori!
Dialogue: 69,0:11:51.17,0:11:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait, Mio.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:53.51,0:11:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How... How'd she get on the other side?
Dialogue: 69,0:12:05.40,0:12:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuck.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:06.50,0:12:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 69,0:12:07.65,0:12:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 69,0:12:09.10,0:12:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we dreamin' or somethin'?
Dialogue: 69,0:12:13.84,0:12:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya goin' after her, Mio?
Dialogue: 69,0:12:15.54,0:12:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,These leather boots cost me 60,000 yen!
Dialogue: 69,0:12:19.33,0:12:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, was that...
Dialogue: 69,0:12:20.92,0:12:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Kofune Mio and Officer Totsumura Tetsu, yes.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:24.57,0:12:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis's premonition might have been right.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:30.63,0:12:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not goin' after 'em. It's a trap.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:33.01,0:12:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But at the very least, Mio is human.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:36.31,0:12:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She has an immunity.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:38.31,0:12:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't blame me, then.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:39.99,0:12:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows what evils lie in wait for us?
Dialogue: 69,0:12:44.70,0:12:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki!
Dialogue: 69,0:12:45.95,0:12:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya've done well to survive after trespassing on sacred ground, Sou.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:49.92,0:12:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me! Wh-What's going on, Tokiko?!
Dialogue: 69,0:12:54.42,0:12:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Too far.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:55.98,0:12:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The nail gun won't reach.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:57.80,0:13:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What are ya doin' here?!
Dialogue: 69,0:13:00.51,0:13:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What a foolish question.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:02.42,0:13:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd ya say?
Dialogue: 69,0:13:03.89,0:13:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to retrieve a defective item.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:06.17,0:13:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya have my thanks for bringing Ushio with ya.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:10.35,0:13:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been hard to find her.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:12.44,0:13:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She's broken, after all.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:14.32,0:13:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's carelessly getting closer.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:16.90,0:13:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Three more steps and she'll be in range.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:18.99,0:13:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:21.32,0:13:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't let ya lay a finger on Ushio!
Dialogue: 69,0:13:29.85,0:13:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please stop!
Dialogue: 69,0:13:38.74,0:13:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Shinpei.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:41.55,0:13:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki's...
Dialogue: 69,0:13:43.53,0:13:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad, Shinpei.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:48.08,0:13:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm human.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:50.20,0:13:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya can kill Shadows, but ya can't kill people, can ya?
Dialogue: 69,0:13:54.77,0:13:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are ya really Tokiko?
Dialogue: 69,0:13:58.96,0:14:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we...
Dialogue: 69,0:14:01.51,0:14:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,have a little chat?
Dialogue: 69,0:14:03.95,0:14:03.99,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:06.41,title,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\c&HC0A038&\blur7}Summer Time Rendering
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.95,0:14:06.41,title,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}Summer Time Rendering
Dialogue: 69,0:14:06.97,0:14:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep asking this of you, Negoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:12.21,signs,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fay-0.01\fs48\fnRaavi\b0\c&H2E2C28&\bord0\pos(1046.14,364.57)\frz0.6282}{TS 14:10}Negoro
Dialogue: 69,0:14:09.93,0:14:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You called, Doctor?
Dialogue: 69,0:14:12.74,0:14:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Add this to their food today.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:16.18,0:14:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost 9 PM.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:17.82,0:14:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and get this to them.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:20.36,0:14:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Doctor.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:21.82,0:14:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:37.78,0:14:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We surrender.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:39.29,0:14:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya gotta be kidding, Shinpei!
Dialogue: 69,0:14:40.78,0:14:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou!
Dialogue: 69,0:14:42.24,0:14:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei's right.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:44.25,0:14:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate to admit it, but we got no chance of winning.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:48.16,0:14:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get any funny ideas, Sou.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:52.29,0:14:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Restrain her.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:57.40,0:14:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio!
Dialogue: 69,0:14:58.40,0:15:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Stop this, Tokiko!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:00.58,0:15:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Sou.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:02.12,0:15:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:03.14,0:15:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If she wanted to kill us, this would've been over already.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:06.13,0:15:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just going to take Ushio with them.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:08.58,0:15:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Toki?
Dialogue: 69,0:15:11.60,0:15:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I still don't understand anything yet.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:15.16,0:15:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll take that silence as a yes.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:18.25,0:15:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In that case, it's still too early.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:21.17,0:15:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry, Ushio. Just a little longer.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:24.09,0:15:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just hang in there for a little longer!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:26.55,0:15:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are ya taking her? To yer father?
Dialogue: 69,0:15:29.45,0:15:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:31.25,0:15:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokiko! Are ya doing this on Dad's orders?
Dialogue: 69,0:15:34.69,0:15:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya don't know anything, Sou.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:37.88,0:15:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course ya don't.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:39.53,0:15:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'weren't chosen by Dad.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:42.17,0:15:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:43.99,0:15:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But now that ya've seen so much,\N it'd be idiotic to keep up the secrecy.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:49.05,0:15:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, this is a good chance to reveal the truth.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:55.25,0:15:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave your belongings here.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:58.38,0:16:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do, I'll show you the way.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:00.79,0:16:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be harmed, so follow me on your own two feet.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:07.34,0:16:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiruko awaits.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:13.05,0:16:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to miss.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:14.68,0:16:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A little to the right. Five degrees to the right.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:16.43,0:16:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind yer own business!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:18.73,0:16:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about me!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:19.72,0:16:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:20.82,0:16:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Focus on yer own targets!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:23.36,0:16:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We've lost sight of Mio.\NIs she okay?
Dialogue: 69,0:16:26.88,0:16:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt this is the time to be worrying about others.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:30.41,0:16:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:31.70,0:16:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell even are we?!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:33.40,0:16:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this, the bottom of the sea?
Dialogue: 69,0:16:36.87,0:16:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a sea anemone.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:40.45,0:16:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Anewhat?
Dialogue: 69,0:16:42.91,0:16:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A deep-sea creature. I saw them on TV long ago.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:47.53,0:16:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for them to live on land.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:50.07,0:16:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible they're all Shadows.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:53.12,0:16:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind us!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:54.90,0:16:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like this.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:58.81,0:17:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeh've killed that thing twice now.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:02.84,0:17:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So how?
Dialogue: 69,0:17:05.01,0:17:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it immortal?!
Dialogue: 69,0:17:06.38,0:17:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? Yer not surprised?
Dialogue: 69,0:17:09.92,0:17:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If we assume you aren't dead, things line up.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:14.04,0:17:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You made me think I killed you and then slipped underground through a crack.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:18.03,0:17:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct?
Dialogue: 69,0:17:19.84,0:17:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister had her suspicions about the sewers.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:22.64,0:17:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd expect nothing less from Hizuru.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:25.05,0:17:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd ya come back?
Dialogue: 69,0:17:27.30,0:17:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I told ya the next time we meet yer dead.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:30.87,0:17:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Do ya still not understand, Minakata Ryuunosuke?
Dialogue: 69,0:17:35.52,0:17:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 69,0:17:36.24,0:17:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No!
Dialogue: 69,0:17:36.83,0:17:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya gave it yer name?!
Dialogue: 69,0:17:38.59,0:17:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized it when we chatted in that child's room.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:41.88,0:17:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine my surprise to learn what was inside Hizuru.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:45.46,0:17:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 69,0:17:46.84,0:17:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Haine?
Dialogue: 69,0:17:50.29,0:17:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been 14 years, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 69,0:17:53.88,0:17:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have no business with you.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:56.38,0:17:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Your personality and memories are all that are here.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:59.56,0:18:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did your body go?
Dialogue: 69,0:18:02.90,0:18:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the body that stole Mother's right eye?
Dialogue: 69,0:18:08.05,0:18:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Haine, you were back to playing pretend from the beginning?
Dialogue: 69,0:18:13.15,0:18:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This time using Kobayakawa Shiori's memories.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:19.64,0:18:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Blocked?
Dialogue: 69,0:18:22.66,0:18:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My bullets should have hit!
Dialogue: 69,0:18:24.37,0:18:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I've read their memories.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:26.31,0:18:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hizuru and Ryuunosuke both don't know where the body is.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:29.68,0:18:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't read the old man.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:31.76,0:18:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I kill them?
Dialogue: 69,0:18:33.04,0:18:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:33.88,0:18:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to run, Ryuunosuke.\NWe're no match for that thing.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:37.46,0:18:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're joking, right?
Dialogue: 69,0:18:38.93,0:18:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't ya tell it's us that's being hunted here?!
Dialogue: 69,0:18:43.09,0:18:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Those aren't Shadows of humans!
Dialogue: 69,0:18:45.27,0:18:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They're something much frightening—\Nsomething entirely different!
Dialogue: 69,0:18:48.48,0:18:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:51.03,0:18:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuunosuke's shifted.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:53.37,0:18:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's shifted about two seconds ahead.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:57.30,0:18:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Understood.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:59.58,0:19:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuunosuke!
Dialogue: 69,0:19:08.38,0:19:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,One down.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:17.40,0:19:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Nezu!
Dialogue: 69,0:19:19.31,0:19:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 69,0:19:22.43,0:19:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 69,0:19:24.99,0:19:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there?
Dialogue: 69,0:19:33.95,0:19:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunate.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:35.25,0:19:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This reading ahead business ain't good.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:41.92,0:19:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are ya going after him?
Dialogue: 69,0:19:43.22,0:19:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No need for that.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:45.64,0:19:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark blood. I must've hit the liver.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:48.95,0:19:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fatal. He'll die eventually if we just leave him alone.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:52.98,0:19:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are Ushio and Shinpei?
Dialogue: 69,0:19:55.11,0:19:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They've gotten far, but don't worry.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:57.96,0:20:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokiko has two wild ones with her.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:00.69,0:20:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:04.02,0:20:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine o'clock needs to come faster.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:13.96,0:20:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn. I can't summon any strength.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:17.66,0:20:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinpei dropped his weapon when he surrendered.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:20.87,0:20:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's because he didn't want to loop when the truth was so close, right?
Dialogue: 69,0:20:26.24,0:20:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You wanna push it as far as you can.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:29.06,0:20:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ain't that right, Shinpei?
Dialogue: 69,0:20:36.02,0:20:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That wasn't me!
Dialogue: 69,0:20:38.76,0:20:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Hiruko. Her stomach rumbles.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:44.97,0:20:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've accepted what I've done.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:49.20,0:20:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't ask for forgiveness.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:51.36,0:20:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All I want now is for y'all to accept things as I have.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:56.97,0:21:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My father was against telling my brother.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:02.24,0:21:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But he needn't have bothered warning me.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:05.83,0:21:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Not like I could tell anyone, anyway.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:08.47,0:21:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, Shinpei.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:10.99,0:21:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't tell Mio.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:13.45,0:21:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're about to see...\NWhat you're about to learn...
Dialogue: 69,0:21:16.88,0:21:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,At least keep it from Mio.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:20.61,0:21:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no intention of getting her involved.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:23.73,0:21:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:25.43,0:21:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer kind, aren't ya?
Dialogue: 69,0:21:32.18,0:21:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The long, long shadow stretched up to the ceiling.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:37.53,0:21:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And at the base...
Dialogue: 69,0:21:48.72,0:21:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nine o'clock.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:52.44,0:21:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to feed.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:55.96,0:21:55.96,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:14.35,0:22:17.36,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,200)}Since I remember it all
Dialogue: 5,0:22:18.32,0:22:21.11,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,200)}I'll alter my existence
Dialogue: 5,0:22:21.11,0:22:23.95,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,200)}Take a breath, take a breath
Dialogue: 5,0:22:23.95,0:22:28.91,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,200)}The smell of a tepid tide, a choir of cicadas
Dialogue: 5,0:22:28.91,0:22:34.33,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,200)}It's not something that can be forgotten
Dialogue: 5,0:22:34.33,0:22:39.84,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,200)}Being torn by engulfing regret is best avoided
Dialogue: 5,0:22:39.84,0:22:44.43,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,200)}So we're setting our lives aflame
Dialogue: 5,0:22:45.64,0:22:55.35,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,200)}I can go on living just from the warmth of your palm if it's linked with mine
Dialogue: 5,0:22:56.56,0:23:07.41,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,200)}What will be left remaining of this all too short summer I wonder
Dialogue: 5,0:23:07.41,0:23:13.91,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,200)}It's once in a lifetime, so we want to undergo a change
Dialogue: 5,0:23:13.91,0:23:18.84,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,2000)}We want to change
